#: _versions/3.34/guides/websockets.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using WebSockets with Undertow"
msgstr "Utilização de WebSockets com o Undertow"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/websockets.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide explains how your Quarkus application can utilize web sockets to create interactive web applications,\n"
"in the context of an Undertow-based Quarkus application, or if you rely on https://jakarta.ee/specifications/websocket/[Jakarta WebSocket]."
msgstr "Este guia explica como sua aplicação Quarkus pode utilizar web sockets para criar aplicações web interativas, no contexto de uma aplicação Quarkus baseada no Undertow ou caso você utilize o link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/websocket/[Jakarta WebSocket] ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/websockets.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you don't use Undertow or https://jakarta.ee/specifications/websocket/[Jakarta WebSocket],\n"
"it is recommended to use the more modern xref:websockets-next-tutorial.adoc[WebSockets Next extensions]."
msgstr "Caso não utilize o Undertow ou link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/websocket/[o Jakarta WebSocket] , recomenda-se o uso das xref:websockets-next-tutorial.adoc[extensões] mais modernas xref:websockets-next-tutorial.adoc[do WebSockets Next] ."

